<plot>Based on a true story, "Nowakowsky: A Forgotten Master" is a dramatic short told through the music of a famous Jewish composer. The short dramatically recreates the time in World War 11 when the music of David Nowakowsky was banned by the Nazis, and his original music sheets were almost lost forever.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?402128</url></doc>
